  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introdução a Opus</title>

    <para>
      <application>Opus</application> is a lossy audio compression format
developed by the Internet Engineering Task Force (IETF) that is particularly
suitable for interactive speech and audio transmission over the
Internet. This package provides the Opus development library and headers.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

